Xchain exchange will be launched on time at 15:00 GMT on September 25, 2024 to open trading.
Xrppproject will stop placing orders at 23:00 GMT on September 24, 2024, and the previous triple returns will continue to be distributed.
During the launch period, Xchain will interact with Xrppproject through the interface, so there will be access restrictions on Xrppproject on September 25, but the restrictions are temporary.
Thank you all members for your understanding and support, let us look forward to a better tomorrow for XRPP.
